Infocast's Project Finance Week continues to be rated the best introductory course on project finance available to developers, financiers, attorneys, utility representatives and vendors. 

Course #1, Project Finance The Tutorial, has been revamped for the new realities of 2002, offering in-depth sessions on today's hottest financing trends, including portfolio financing, synthetic leasing, and risk management strategies for merchant financing. These in-depth sessions will be enhanced by hearing the lessons learned by active participants in many of the top project financings of 2001.

? The Contractor's Perspective On Construction,Completion And Performance Risk
